<p>Convenient walking distance from CTA Diversey #76, Ashland #9 and Belmont #77 buses.</p>
<p>CTA Brown, Purple &amp; Red Line Trains stop at the Belmont Station, 945 W. Belmont, where you can hop on the #77 Belmont bus WEST (towards Sheffield) to Ashland Ave. Short walk from there, SOUTH on Ashland past Central Savings Bank to 3040 N. Ashland.</p>
<p>The CTA Brown Line Train also stops at the Paulina Station, 3410 N. Lincoln Ave., 0.5 miles from the gallery. Walk SE on Lincoln to Belmont/Lincoln/Ashland (6-Corners) and continue SOUTH on Ashland, past Central Savings Bank to 3040 N. Ashland.</p>
