<p>-Open Galleries &#8211;<a href="https://www.tigerstrikesasteroid.com/chi/debra-kayes-i-seem-to-be-a-verb" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Tiger Strikes Asteroid Chicago</a>,<a href="https://www.purplewindowgallery.com/?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnWSpGad0VS0pKEmH4FZ3008KnjC11xiheeQa0gCdlUHsHKrj70TM5apYCVzA_aem_pY0WbtyIks2qinrnUkZJfA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Purple Window Gallery</a></p>
