The filmmaker and artists iwll be at the John David Mooney Foundation to dicuss the film after the screening, and the Consul General of Ireland, Brian Cahalane, will open the evening&#8217;s celebration.</p>
<p>This screening is in collaboration with The Chicago Irish Film Festival.</p>
