<p>Edinho’s mastery of the 7-string and 12-string guitars provides a lush harmonic landscape for Ana’s voice &#8211; brilliant, nuanced, and rich in color &#8211; and her inventive use of electronics, including looping and effects that evoke children’s choirs, monastic chants, and echoes from the depths of nature. Ana leads the project with original compositions inspired by her homeland, the Republic of Moldova.</p>
<p>Together, they create a deeply expressive sound, rooted in tradition and shaped by contemporary textures.</p>
